Package: crsuggest
Type: Package
Title: Obtain Suggested Coordinate Reference System Information for Spatial Data
Version: 0.2
Date: 2021-04-30
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Kyle", family = "Walker", 
           email="kyle@walker-data.com", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Uses data from the EPSG Registry to look up suitable coordinate reference 
    system transformations for spatial datasets in R.  Returns a data frame with CRS codes
    that can be used for CRS transformation and mapping with coord_sf() in ggplot2.  Please see 
    the EPSG Dataset Terms of Use at http://www.epsg.org/TermsOfUse.aspx for more information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  sf (>= 0.9),
  dplyr,
  purrr,
  mapview
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
